</a><br/><br/>Scandalous and scintillating, <i>The Monk</i> is a literary marvel.</span>
  <span id="freeText4498522099505918653" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f34XzCtirjg" rel="nofollow noopener">Click here</a> to watch a video review of this book on my BookTube channel, <i>From Beginning to Bookend</i>.<br><br><a href="https://imgur.com/6kLHT7y" rel="nofollow noopener">
